  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca 1400\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 with 1400 liters of petrol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "1429 liters of petrol, which was being illegally transported from Halawata to Kalpitiya in a refrigerated lorry, was seized by the Norochchola Police and the Navy in Dalua area early today (18th).",
        "The driver and assistant of the lorry along with the fuel stock have also been arrested.",
        "According to the information received by the Navy, the arrest was made during an immediate roadblock operated by the Norochchola Police and the Navy.",
        "The two suspects, aged 26 and 29, are residents of Halawatha Mugunawatawana and Reedi Wella areas. It has been reported that they have been engaged in fuel smuggling for some time.",
        "The suspects are to be produced in Puttalam Magistrate's Court. Norochchola Police is conducting further investigations."
      ],
